ly coupled layers, a local scaling approximation is used,\nand we find that the magnetically ordered state exhibits a lattice of magnetic\nvortices, with the lattice constant tunable through the twisting angle.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 20 Apr 2022 18:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 12 Oct 2022 16:39:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-09"}
