mMC outperforms most state-of-the-art skeleton-based methods. We\nfurther show its scalability and efficiency in enhancing the performance of\nexisting models. Our codes are available at https://github.com/Kali-Hac/SimMC.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Apr 2022 00:19:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 28 Apr 2022 00:38:05 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 12 Jun 2022 04:12:20 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sun, 19 Jun 2022 05:15:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-22"}
