onal pressure and flow with increasing degree of stenosis,\nas expected. The benchmark data set is made available to the research\ncommunity, with the purpose to validate and compare in-silico models of\ndifferent type.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Apr 2022 10:07:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-22"}
